quran[26]{c,v,t}:
  42,51,"Onyankopͻn nkasa nkyerε onipa gyesε Ɔdefa Adiyisεm so, anaasε ntwaremu bi akyi, anaasε Ɔsoma Bͻfoͻ wͻ Netumi mu ma no beyi deε Ɔpε no kyerε no. Nokorε sε Ɔne Otumfoͻ a Ɔkorͻn, Ɔne Onyansafoͻ"
  42,52,"Saa ara na Yε’nam Yε’tumi so ayi Honhom no (Qur’aan) ama woͻ. Na anka wonnim deε yεfrε no Nwoma no, anaasε gyidie. Na mmom Y’ayε Qur’aan yi nhyerεnee, Yε’de kyerε Yεn nkoa no mu nea Yε’pε kwan. Nokorε sε wo kyerε (amanfoͻ) kwan kͻ kwan tenenee no so"
  42,53,Onyankopͻn a ͻsoro ne asaase wͻ no no kwan no so. Nokorε sε Onyankopͻn hͻ na nsεm nyinaa san kͻwie
  43,1,Haa – Miim
  43,2,Mede Nwoma no a εda (biribiara) adi pefee no di nse sε
  43,3,"Nokorε, Y’ayε Qur’aan no wͻ Arab kasa mu sεdeε mobεte aseε"
  43,4,"Efiri Nwoma (nyinaa) Maame (Lawhul- Mah’fuuz) a εwͻ Yε’nkyεn no mu, (Nwoma a) yamaso paa, adwen ne nyansa ahyε mma"
  43,5,Enti Yenyi afutuo no mfri moso εnam sε moyε nnipa bͻnefoͻ nti
  43,6,Nkͻmhyεfoͻ dodoͻ sεn na Yε’somaa wͻn baa tetefoͻ no hͻ
  43,7,Nkͻmhyεni a ᴐbaa wᴐn hᴐ biara gyesε wͻ’di ne ho fεw
  43,8,Y’asεe wͻn a wͻ’yε den sen wͻn wͻ ahoͻden mu; na tetefoͻ no mfatoho adi wͻn anim kan atwam kͻ
  43,9,"Sε wo bisa wͻn nso sε: “Hwan na ͻbͻͻ soro ne asaase a? “Wͻ’bεka sε: “Otumfoͻ Onimdefoͻ no na Ɔbͻeε”"
  43,10,"(Otumfoͻ) no a, W’ayε asaase de asε hͻ atrε mu ama mo, ayε akwan atoto mu sεdeε mobehunu kwan"
  43,11,"(Onyankopͻn) no a Osiane nsuo firi soro sεdeε εsε, na Y’εde nyane asaase a awuo; saa ara na monso mobepue (afri adakamena mu)"
  43,12,"(Otumfoͻ) no a Ɔbͻͻ biribiara mmienu mmienu, εna W’ama mo nsuom hyεn ne nyεmmoa a mo foro (tena wᴐn soᴐ)"
  43,13,"Sεdeε mobεtena wͻn akyi pintinn, na afei mobεkae Onyankopͻn adom wͻ εberε a mote so pintinn no na moaka sε: “Kronkron Hene ne Nea W’abrε woi ase ama yεn, na anka (yεn ara yεn mmͻdemmͻ mma) yentumi nya"
  43,14,Nokorε sε ye’Wura Nyankopͻn hͻ na yε’bεsan akͻ
  43,15,Nanso wͻ’de kyεfa bi a εwͻ no ama Nenkoa mu no bi. Nokorε sε onipa yε boniayεni pefee
  43,16,"Anaasε Onyankopͻn Ayi mmaa (ama Neho) wͻ deε W’abͻ no mu, εna W’ayi mmarima ama mo"
  43,17,"Nanso sε yε’bͻ wͻn mu bi amaneε wͻ adeε a ͻdema Nyankopͻn no sεso (sε neyere awo ͻbaa) a na n’anim ayε kusuu (wamuna tumm), na nebo afu"
  43,18,"Anaasε deε yεde afεεfεdeε asiesie no a sε akyinnyeε ba a, ontumi nkasa nkyerεkyerε mu no (na mode no toto Onyankopͻn ho)"
  43,19,"(Abosomsomfoͻ no) ayε Ahummͻborͻ Hene asomfoͻ Soro abͻfoͻ no nso mmaa. Wͻ’ahunu (Soro abͻfoͻ no) bͻsuo (pεn a enti εma wͻ’kyerε sε soro abͻfoͻ yε mmaa)? Yε’bεtwerε wͻn adanse-kunumu no, na yebebisa wͻn"
  43,20,"Deε wͻ’ka ne sε: “Sε Ahummͻborͻ Hene no pε a anka yε’nsom wͻn”. Wͻ’nni woi ho nimdeε, atorͻsεm na wͻ’die"
  43,21,Anaasε Y’adi kan ama wͻn nwoma bi a wͻ’gyina soͻ
  43,22,"Daabi; Deε wͻ’ka ne sε: “Yε’bεtoo yεn agyanom wͻ (saa) kwan no so, na wͻn anammͻn so na εkyerε yεn kwan"
  43,23,"Saa ara na kͻkͻbͻni biara a Y’edii w’anim kan somaa no wͻ kuro bi soͻ no, emu adefoͻ no kaa sε: “Nokorε sε yεbεtoo y’agyanom wͻ (saa) kwan (yi) so na wͻn anammͻn so na yε’di akyire"